OBJECTIVE: kill all ALIENS.

 each player controls 1 marine in heavy armour. simply hunt
down and kill all the aliens until a >SECTOR CLEAR> message
appears at the top of  the screen.  then press >f1> to end
the mission.
            ------------------------------------
USING EQUIPMENT:
 if a marine is carrying a manually operable equipment item
 equipment< such as a medi-kit< it will appear in the fifth
 @ sixth slots on the control panel. (the lower box is for
 player 2).
 you can also use the control panel at the bottom of the
 screen. left click to use an item< and right click to cycle
 through the 3 equipment slots.

 there is also a keyboard shortcut. press >S> or >J>(ply2)
 to use the currently selected equipment item.
            ------------------------------------
WEAPON: both the marines are equipped with a rotary assault
 weapon.(r.a.w.) this is a cut-down version of the chain gun.
 it is very powerful but has a low range and poor accuracy.
 it also consumes ammunition very rapidly.

EQUIPMENT: the marines have 3 equipment slots. these contain
 a mapper< which plots where they have been< a scanner which
 shows the aliens @ a medi-kit.


  -     area >a>     :-              -   deployment zone.  -
  -  yellow arrows   :-              -  alien entry points.- 

